    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs mt-2">
    <p>
      Your membership expired on
      <b class="font-semibold">{{format-date @user.activeSubscription.endDate}}</b>. Start a new membership to get access to
